# Logic Engine

- Build catalog: `python3 services/logic-engine/scripts/build_registry.py` with repo-root and packages config as documented in README.
- Run API: `python3 services/logic-engine/scripts/run_api.py` (port via env as in unified runbook).
- Retention: `run_retention_worker.py` when touching lifecycle policies.
- Keep generated outputs under `services/logic-engine/generated/` consistent with scripts; prefer regenerating over hand-editing JSON catalogs.
